content:
This build was released on the 10th of December, 2023.
It is known as starstruck because it adds many stars to the game.

General Changes:
 - Wf.z64's red star is back, and The Star's red star is now a normal star.
 - Genesis Basement's green star is back, and the post-game stars have become green. An extra red coin green star has been added in World of Dreams.
 - Additional stars have been added which utilize unused star IDs and post-game star IDs. These will already show up as collected if you've collected the post-game stars in a previous Unabandoned version. The aditional stars' list can be found in the changelog.
